summary: Geologist with additional knowledge of ecology, environment, and geographical information systems. Skilled in writing texts for multiple purposes, such as scientific publications, feasibility studies, educational texts, user manuals, online Help, brochures, and magazine articles. Specialties: Pull-apart tectonics, mass flow sedimentology, underground storage of carbon dioxide, geothermal energy, groundwater and geological information systems
